snippet.title: Casino Resort Tower is coming to Steam Early Access!
snippet.description:
Casino Resort Tower is a simulation game where you build and manage a casino hotel skyscraper from the ground up. While trying to solve the problems caused by troublesome customers with a CEO that dreams about a luxury office.

Wishlist Now On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1457030/Casino_Resort_Tower/

Casino Resort Tower Discord: https://discord.gg/2y5eXn3ubs

Twitter: https://twitter.com/CasinoRsrtTower
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/CasinoResortTower/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CasinoResortTower
